e":"2021-01-15T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"吹左廿年新世界秩序架構成型了,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"New World Order<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9522a103553e580baf8e397bf84c97706ad4ec64","tid":2367394,"uid":350242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"410fc08c9da772369ce6f344deeb09d0662a387f","tid":2367394,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5492001089c2945ed39c3b2919ed72f90ac7eb","tid":2367394,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"吹左廿年新世界秩序架構成型了,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"New World Order<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"光明會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1841d953810e2d23bbe5375354fa04e5bff6904","tid":2367394,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9522a103553e580baf8e397bf84c97706ad4ec64","tid":2367394,"uid":350242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"410fc08c9da772369ce6f344deeb09d0662a387f","tid":2367394,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5492001089c2945ed39c3b2919ed72f90ac7eb","tid":2367394,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"吹左廿年新世界秩序架構成型了,<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"New World Order<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"光明會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:45:42.000Z","msg":"而家侵係阻止呢件事發生 但係對面班big tech 金權勢力明顯冇底線 咩手續都用曬 就係要將侵呢個人趕走 <br />\n<br />\n好快地球就好似日本高達片咁 得返地球聯邦政府(金權勢力)"},{"pid":"67b009477b39d57507086c13a97b57389073f08d","tid":2367394,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211ffeddf18cfe760aaa85b7c1d7d18c3b98454a","tid":2367394,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7accd9a3dad2c830d2fae2f1826ae36233b03de","tid":2367394,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"快啲reset<br />\n咁既垃圾世界我就唔想要<br />\n又唔公平 又冇正義 又冇民主<br />\n世界毀滅最好"}]}